the enterprise which covers an area of 15,000 square meters.
Products manufactured by the company will be used in computers,
mobile phones, TVs and washing machines.
</P>
<P>
Philips has also planned to invest 1 billion yuan to expand the
enterprise's production in the next two years.
</P>
<P>
The Netherlands-based company has already sponsored 32 solely
funded and Sino-Netherlands joint-venture enterprises in China,
with a total investment exceeding 1 billion US dollars. 
