Samaria division of the Israeli Defense Forces (IDF) submitted his
resignation over last Saturday night's botched Duvdevan commando
raid that resulted in the deaths of three soldiers and the escape
of key Islamic militant Hamas fugitive Mahmoud Abu-Hanoud.
</P>
