<HEADLINE> New Zealand Stocks Finish Lower </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WELLINGTON, September 1 (Xinhua) -- The New Zealand sharemarket
closed lower here Friday.
</P>
<P>
The NZSE40 Index ended 10 points lower at 2,083 with a turnover
of 179.1 million NZ dollars (76.3 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
